程序包 org.janusgraph.diskstorage.util

类 StaticArrayBuffer

java.lang.Object
org.janusgraph.diskstorage.util.StaticArrayBuffer
所有已实现的接口:
Comparable<StaticBuffer>, StaticBuffer
直接已知子类:
ReadArrayBuffer, StaticArrayEntry
public class StaticArrayBuffer
extends Object
implements StaticBuffer
Implementation of StaticBuffer against byte array.

The byte to primitive conversion code was copied from / is inspired by Kryo's Input class: https://code.google.com/p/kryo/source/browse/trunk/src/com/esotericsoftware/kryo/io/Input.java

作者:
Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
